%N A383834 Sum of the legs of the unique primitive Pythagorean triple whose inradius is A000217(n) and such that its long leg and its hypotenuse are consecutive natural numbers.
%D A383834 Miguel Ángel Pérez García-Ortega, José Manuel Sánchez Muñoz and José Miguel Blanco Casado, El Libro de las Ternas Pitagóricas, Preprint 2025.
%H A383834 Andrew Howroyd, <a href="/A383834/b383834.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
